<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَنْ نَذَرَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> الصَّدَقَةَ بِكُلِّ مَالِهِ:</span> أَجْزَأَهُ ثُلُثُهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> أَوْ صَوْمَ شَهْرٍ وَنَحْوِهِ:</span> لَزِمَهُ التَّتَابُعُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- لَا إِنْ نَذَرَ أَيَّاماً مَعْدُودَةً.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَسُنَّ <span class="c2">(١)</span> الوَفَاءُ بِالوَعْدِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَحَرُمَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> بِلَا اسْتِثْنَاءٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (د): (ويسن).<br>(٢) في (د): ويحرم.</p> </div>